title: Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015 KPBS Evening Edition KPBS San Diego
text: As Solana Beach considers banning plastic foam food containers, some restaurant owners say their bottom line could be hurt. Plus, San Diego's farm-to-school program expands and the San Diego Museum of Art examines the "The Art of Music."
